name: Memory Transfer 11457
description: The memory associated with this moment now resides in this object. The original has been transferred to this state by form of replacement/reinstallation/destruction. The black components are necessary for the brain to reassociate with the replaced memory, thus over-writing the former. They also act as a validation/credibility checker with the transferred memory; a form of mental proof via differentiation. This NFT over time will become a stronger memory in this digital landscape, than the internal one of it's original occupier. It is the first transfer of memory by this artist.
